&lt;h3 id=&#34;19-es7-reactreduxgraphqlreact-native-snippets&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#19-es7-reactreduxgraphqlreact-native-snippets&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 19、ES7 React/Redux/GraphQL/React-Native snippets&lt;/h3&gt;
